<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vegan Café Menu</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f1ea;
            color: #4e342e;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #6d4c41;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .menu-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #795548;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #6d4c41;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .menu-item {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .menu-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .menu-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #5d4037;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .menu-item p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        Vegan Café Menu
    </header>

    <div class="menu-container">
        <h2>Breakfast</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Avocado Toast <span>₹180</span></h3>
            <p>Mashed avocado on whole-grain toast with cherry tomatoes & seeds.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Chia Pudding <span>₹150</span></h3>
            <p>Chia seeds soaked in plant-based milk, sweetened naturally.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Tofu Scramble <span>₹160</span></h3>
            <p>Scrambled tofu with turmeric and veggies.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Vegan Pancakes <span>₹200</span></h3>
            <p>Fluffy pancakes made with almond milk & flax eggs.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Main Courses</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Vegan Buddha Bowl <span>₹250</span></h3>
            <p>Quinoa, roasted veggies, chickpeas, avocado, tahini dressing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Lentil Soup <span>₹180</span></h3>
            <p>Hearty soup with lentils, tomatoes, and warming spices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Stuffed Bell Peppers <span>₹220</span></h3>
            <p>Peppers filled with quinoa, beans, and tomato sauce.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Chickpea Salad Sandwich <span>₹170</span></h3>
            <p>Mashed chickpeas with vegan mayo, mustard & celery.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Snacks</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Roasted Chickpeas <span>₹100</span></h3>
            <p>Crunchy and spiced for a protein boost.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Guacamole & Tortilla Chips <span>₹180</span></h3>
            <p>Fresh avocado dip with lime and tomatoes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Vegan Spring Rolls <span>₹200</span></h3>
            <p>Rice paper rolls with veggies & tofu, served with peanut sauce.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Desserts</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Vegan Brownies <span>₹150</span></h3>
            <p>Fudgy, chocolatey, and made with almond flour.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Dairy-Free Ice Cream <span>₹180</span></h3>
            <p>Made with frozen bananas and coconut milk.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Vegan Cheesecake <span>₹220</span></h3>
            <p>No-bake cheesecake with cashews and coconut cream.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
